Section 3.1(q)
(without giving effect to the Knowledge qualification contained therein), such approval constitutes approval of the Merger, the Share Issuance and the other transactions contemplated hereby by the Board of Directors of IDEC under the provisions of Section 203 of the Delaware General Corporation Law ("
Section 203
") such that Section 203 does not apply to this Agreement, the Share Issuance and the other transactions contemplated hereby. To the Knowledge of IDEC, no state takeover statute other than Section 203 (which has been rendered inapplicable) is applicable to the Merger, the Share Issuance or the other transactions contemplated hereby.
        (o)
