        (r)
    Material Contracts.
    
        (i)    For purposes of this Agreement, "
IDEC Material Contract
" shall mean:
        (1)   any "material contracts" (as such term is used in Item 601(b)(10) of Regulation S-K of the SEC) with respect to IDEC and its Subsidiaries;
