[CONFIDENTIAL TREATMENT REQUESTED]
of Genentech's costs in acquiring the rights in the United States to such product under such agreement with such Third Party
[CONFIDENTIAL TREATMENT REQUESTED]
. The Parties shall seek to agree on the amount of such opt-in fee, and to the extent the Parties are unable to agree within a twenty (20) day period, such dispute shall be subject to Section 17.2.
