[CONFIDENTIAL TREATMENT REQUESTED]
.
        (b)   In addition, Genentech shall have the right, at its election, to
[CONFIDENTIAL TREATMENT REQUESTED]
as follows:
        (i)    Genentech shall provide written notice to IDEC of the specific date upon which
[CONFIDENTIAL TREATMENT REQUESTED]
(such notice to be provided at least
[CONFIDENTIAL TREATMENT REQUESTED]
);
        (ii)   To the extent
[CONFIDENTIAL TREATMENT REQUESTED]
; and
        (iii)  To the extent
