     The press release attached as Exhibit 99.1 includes information with respect to the Registrant's adjusted non-GAAP earnings per share and net income for the first quarter of 2005 and 2004. These are non-GAAP financial measures. The non-GAAP financial measures exclude non-cash merger-related accounting impacts and other merger-related charges.
