Section 6.1(b)
     (d) If a determination shall have been made pursuant to this that the claimant is entitled to indemnification, the corporation shall be bound by such determination in any judicial proceeding commenced pursuant to above. The corporation shall be precluded from asserting in any judicial proceeding commenced pursuant to above that the procedures and presumptions of this are not valid, binding and enforceable and shall stipulate in such proceeding that the corporation is bound by all the provisions of this .
