     You hereby irrevocably waive any claim against any person or entity in connection with any alleged non-compliance with the provisions of Section 4(b) of the Employment Agreement or Section 4.3 or Article 9 of the Company's Amended and Restated Bylaws. You further waive your rights under the last sentence of Section 2(a) of the Employment Agreement.
