ITEM 5.02.   DEPARTURE OF DIRECTORS OR PRINCIPAL OFFICERS; ELECTION OF DIRECTORS; APPOINTMENT OF PRINCIPAL OFFICERS.
       On June 29, 2007, Biogen Idec Inc. announced the resignation of Executive Vice President, Finance and Chief Financial Officer Peter Kellogg. A copy of the press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and its contents are incorporated herein by reference.
ITEM 9.01   FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND EXHIBITS.
