Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
     On February 6, 2009, Biogen Idec Inc. issued a press release announcing its results of operations and financial condition for the full year and three months ended December 31, 2008. A copy of the press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 and is incorporated herein by reference.
