Affiliate, as of the record date for the 2010 Annual Meeting, to be present for quorum purposes and to be voted, at the 2010 Annual Meeting or at any adjournments or postponements thereof, in favor of the directors nominated by the Board for election at the 2010 Annual Meeting which shall include the New Class 1 Directors and no more than two other nominees.
