Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
     On February 1, 2011, Biogen Idec Inc. issued a press release announcing its results of operations and financial condition for the full year and three months ended December 31, 2010. A copy of the press release is furnished as Exhibit 99 and is incorporated herein by reference.
