2.1.
    
Term
. This Agreement shall be effective as of the Execution Date and shall, unless earlier terminated in accordance with its terms, remain in effect in perpetuity (the 
Term
). The Parties obligations under this Section 2, Sections 3.4 through 3.7, Section 3.11(e), Section 3.11(f),
