4.1.
    
Upfront Payment
. Subject to the terms and conditions of this Agreement, Biogen Idec shall make a one-time payment to Elan at the Closing of three billion, two hundred forty-nine million dollars ($3,249,000,000) plus the Estimated Closing Date Inventory Value set forth in the statement referred to in the first sentence of Section 4.8 (together, the 
Upfront Payment
), which payment shall be irrevocable, non-refundable and non-creditable toward any other payments due to Elan.
4.2.
    
Contingent Payments
.
(a)
    
Subject to the terms and conditions of this Agreement, Biogen Idec or its designated Affiliates shall pay to Elan, with respect to aggregate Net Sales in all countries in the Territory during the twelve (12) month period beginning on the first day of the first full calendar month after the Closing Date (the 
Initial Contingent Payment Period
), twelve percent (12%) of aggregate Net Sales during such period in all countries in the Territory.
