Subject to the terms and conditions of this Agreement, Biogen Idec or its designated Affiliates shall pay to Elan, with respect to aggregate Net Sales in all countries in the Territory during the period (if any) beginning on the first day after the end of the Initial Contingent Payment Period and ending on December 31, 2014, the following amounts:
